#### Staff Software Engineer, Dev Infra
https://careers.airbnb.com/positions/6000539/

You will be joining as a Tech Lead engineer on the Client Testing Platform team. This team is part of the Developer Infrastructure group at Airbnb.

As an tech lead on this team, you’ll work with the EM to define the team's technical strategy, roadmap and goals. You will also be responsible to maintain trusting relationships with customer, peer and stakeholder teams in the US and will also be responsible for mentoring ICs on the team.

As a software engineer in this team, you’ll work on test infrastructure to enable integration testing, performance testing, differential testing etc. Your responsibilities will include designing, implementing and maintaining this  infrastructure, improving system stability and avoiding test flakiness etc.

- 9+ years of industry experience
- Bachelor’s and/or Master’s degree, preferably in CS, or equivalent experience
- Proficiency in one or more back-end server languages (Java/Go/Kotlin)
- Experience leading and shipping large scope technical projects in collaboration with multiple experienced engineers.
- Familiarity with test system that serves large engineering group (1000+)
- Experience or knowledge of front-end, Android or iOS development will be better.
- Fluent English and Mandarin in oral and written communication

关于position：
- CSP的具体内容
- 面向客户
- Infra呢
- Staff和Senior还有senior staff 对应amazon的level

关于工作内容和技术栈:

- 团队主要负责哪些系统和项目?目前面临的主要技术挑战是什么?
- 系统架构和技术栈的选择(比如云平台、开发语言、主要框架等)?
- 对系统可靠性、性能和安全性的要求如何?
- 日常工作中需要跟美国团队协作的频率有多高?时差如何协调?

关于团队和管理:

- 团队规模和人员组成情况?直属领导的管理风格?
- 技术决策的流程是怎样的?工程师在技术方案选择上的自主权如何?
- 团队的代码审查、上线发布等工程实践是怎样的?
- 加班情况如何?是否有弹性工作制?

关于职业发展:

- 这个职位的职级和晋升体系是怎样的?晋升评估的主要标准是什么?
- 公司是否有轮岗机制?有机会接触不同的技术领域吗?
- 团队的培训机制如何?是否有导师制?
- 是否有机会参与开源项目或技术分享?

关于公司文化和福利:

- 公司的技术文化是怎样的?是否重视创新和工程师成长?
- 薪资结构如何(基本工资、年终奖、期权等)?
- 五险一金的缴纳基数?是否有补充医疗保险?
- 年假天数?是否有带薪病假?

其他重要问题:
- 目前团队最急需解决的问题或挑战是什么?
- 作为海外回流的工程师,有什么特别需要注意或适应的地方?
- 公司对未来3-5年的技术发展规划是怎样的?
- 招聘流程和面试关注点是什么?


